<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1><%= heading %></h1>
  </header>
  
  <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
  
  <main>
    <section id="about">
      <h2>About Me</h2>
      <p>Welcome to my homepage! I'm a passionate web developer and I love creating amazing websites.</p>
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/200" alt="Profile Picture" width="200" height="200">
    </section>
    
    <section id="services">
      <h2>Services</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Web Design</li>
        <li>Web Development</li>
        <li>Responsive Design</li>
        <li>Website Maintenance</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    
    <section id="portfolio">
      <h2>Portfolio</h2>
      <div class="gallery">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Project 1" width="300" height="200">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Project 2" width="300" height="200">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Project 3" width="300" height="200">
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="blog">
      <h2>Latest Blog Posts</h2>
      <article>
        <h3>Blog Post 1</h3>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ac nisi vel purus luctus aliquet. Mauris lacinia suscipit turpis id efficitur.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Blog Post 2</h3>
        <p>Nulla facilisi. Donec ut tellus vitae massa vestibulum suscipit. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Mauris vestibulum mauris vitae lectus tempor, et ullamcorper erat ultrices.</p>
      </article>
      
      <!-- Create Blog Form -->
      <div class="create-blog-form">
        <h3>Create Blog</h3>
        <form>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="title">Title</label>
            <input type="text" id="title" name="title" placeholder="Enter the blog title" required>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="content">Content</label>
            <textarea id="content" name="content" placeholder="Enter the blog content" rows="8" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="tags">Tags</label>
            <input type="text" id="tags" name="tags" placeholder="Enter tags for the blog (comma-separated)">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="submit" value="Create Blog" class="btn">
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
      <!-- End of Create Blog Form -->
    </section>
    
    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Me</h2>
        <p>You can reach out to me via email at <a href="mailto:example@example.com">example@example.com</a>.</p>
        <p>Follow me on social media:</p>
        <ul class="social-media">
            <li><a href="https://www.twitter.com">Twitter</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com">Facebook</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com">Instagram</a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <img src="/static/imageOne.png" alt="">
  
  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>

</body>
</html>
